Docker version 28.2.2, build 28.2.2-0ubuntu1~24.04.1

$ which docker
/usr/bin/docker

$ date
Sun Oct 26 10:46:03 AM PDT 2025
</code></pre>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Docker Build Configuration</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li>✓ Docker 28.2.2 installed and operational</li>
                <li>✓ Docker daemon accessible</li>
